d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb330f7b82a0d89863d0c7a087e57aeb220a35f1","tid":56452,"uid":14461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T21:01:07.000Z","msg":"睇左兩次兩次都暈到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc02665bad937bea512e210ec278304ac757a6d3","tid":56452,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T21:24:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有睇 超神！今年睇過最深刻嘅電影<br />\n但唔識技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n劇情討論都可以 套戲上半同下半完全兩樣野<br />\n但係好smooth  後半好緊張<br />\n演員演得好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce9f0b2f3088b82950aaafd7fba4be7610b4e8d","tid":56452,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T21:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇左兩次兩次都暈到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你都好鍾意套戲 睇兩次<br />\nBtw我唔覺暈 反而好鍾意佢嘅拍攝手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015191e5eef8e43b2b892fdb2421f302aecf4e44","tid":56452,"uid":14461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T21:32:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇左兩次兩次都暈到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你都好鍾意套戲 睇兩次<br />\nBtw我唔覺暈 反而好鍾意佢嘅拍攝手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係因為遲左成半個鐘入場先睇多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都要值得睇先會睇多次嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd75501619f0ca9f9ac2e5f2b71b79d9fe28a23","tid":56452,"uid":2025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:49:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有睇 超神！今年睇過最深刻嘅電影<br />\n但唔識技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n劇情討論都可以 套戲上半同下半完全兩樣野<br />\n但係好smooth  後半好緊張<br />\n演員演得好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我反而鐘意前半多d, 後半太誇張<br />\n但一鏡的確值得一睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3147250b53e421e4896f0dfb8ae4f37e9be1205a","tid":56452,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:51:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有睇 超神！今年睇過最深刻嘅電影<br />\n但唔識技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n劇情討論都可以 套戲上半同下半完全兩樣野<br />\n但係好smooth  後半好緊張<br />\n演員演得好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我反而鐘意前半多d, 後半太誇張<br />\n但一鏡的確值得一睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前半會以為係普通寫實愛情片<br />\n後半對比前半嘅寫實 係有啲誇<br />\n但係戲劇發展來講 推進幾流暢<br />\n尾段有迫力<br />\n<br />\n一鏡嘅技術 真係值得睇<br />\n比birdman有過之無不及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}